== How to update the firmware in TellStick Net using Mac OS X ==

Download and run the TellStickNetFlasher-utility.[[BR]]
[http://download.telldus.com/TellStick/Software/TellStickNetFlasher/TellStickNetFlasher.dmg]
[[BR]][[BR]][[BR]]
If you experience any problems with the TellStickNetFlasher-utility, please try this guide instead: 
[http://developer.telldus.com/wiki/Firmware_mac_terminal]

